to a fourth offense of driving under the influence as described for in proposed
law.
The Committee Amendments Proposed by House Committee on Appropriations to the
engrossed bill:
1. Adds exceptions to present law penalties for certain subsequent offenses if
proposed law applies.
2. Make technical changes.
